      1369,
      1395
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\frac{1}{KH^2} = \\frac{1}{AH^2} + \\frac{1}{A'H^2} \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{2}{3} \\cdot \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right)^2} = \\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{3}\\right)^2} + \\frac{1}{A'H^2} \\Rightarrow A'H = \\frac{2}{3}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      203,
      1415,
      813,
      1457
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Thể tích của khối lăng trụ $ABC.A'B'C'$ là"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      533,
      1464,
      1162,
      1552
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nV = S_{ABC} \\cdot A'H = \\frac{2^2\\sqrt{3}}{4} \\cdot \\frac{2}{3} = \\frac{2\\sqrt{3}}{3} \\approx 1,15.\n$$"
  },
